---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
const playStoreUrl = 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=it.sherlock.polizze';
---
<footer class="bg-navy-900 border-t border-navy-800 mt-20">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 py-12 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
    <div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-gold-400 to-gold-600 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-4 h-4 text-navy-900" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="7" />
            <line x1="16" y1="16" x2="21" y2="21" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span class="notranslate font-extrabold text-white" translate="no">Sherlock</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-navy-400 leading-relaxed">
        Il detective delle tue polizze assicurative. Capisci cosa firmi,
        contesta ciò che non torna.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs text-navy-500 mt-4">
        Sherlock è uno strumento di analisi AI. <strong class="text-navy-300">Non sostituisce un avvocato o un consulente assicurativo</strong>:
        è un'assistenza informativa per orientarti e generare bozze di reclamo da
        rivedere prima dell'invio.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-navy-500 mb-3">Sito</div>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-navy-300">
        <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-white">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/abbonati" class="hover:text-white">Abbonamento</a></li>
        <li><a href="/guide" class="hover:text-white">Guide</a></li>
        <li><a href="/esempio-report" class="hover:text-white">Esempio report</a></li>
        <li><a href="/esempio-lettera" class="hover:text-white">Esempio lettera</a></li>
        <li><a href="/trasparenza" class="hover:text-white">Trasparenza dati</a></li>
        <li><a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-white">Privacy</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-navy-500 mb-3">Prova Sherlock</div>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-navy-300">
        <li>
          <a href="/app/" class="hover:text-white">
            Apri dal browser (Web/iPhone) →
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href={playStoreUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-white">
            Scarica gratis su Google Play →
          </a>
        </li>
        <li class="text-navy-500 text-xs pt-2">it.sherlock.polizze</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t border-navy-800 px-5 py-5 max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-3 text-xs text-navy-500">
    <div class="notranslate" translate="no">© {year} Sherlock — ScapLAB</div>
    <div>Sviluppato in Italia 🇮🇹</div>
  </div>
</footer>
